data.description: Step into this delightful, fully detached two-family home, impeccably maintained and nestled in a serene neighborhood. This treasure showcases a personal driveway and an expansive backyard, complete with a deck/patio-ideal for hosting BBQs, unwinding on the deck, or savoring a morning coffee/tea on the patio. The sizable 30 x 100 lot provides abundant space for various activities. Each unit boasts three bedrooms and one bath, ensuring cozy living spaces for both families. The open-concept kitchen and living room layout elevate the overall charm of this dwelling. Conveniently positioned near transportation options and local establishments, this property strikes the perfect balance between comfort and accessibility. With low taxes, seize the chance to transform this house into your new home!
